references: A. Brousseau, Fibonacci and Related Number Theoretic Tables. Fibonacci Association, San Jose, CA, 1972, p. 88.
formula: Fibonomial coefficients formed from sequence F_3k [ 2, 8, 34, ... ].a(n, k) = product(fibonacci(2*(n-j)), j=0..k-1)/product(fibonacci(2*j), j=1..k)
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
extensions: More terms from _James A. Sellers_, Feb 09 2000
